%% Diagram 02 — Sinkronisasi logLine di GeoProcessor
%% Simbol: ([ ]) Terminator | [ ] Proses | { } Keputusan
flowchart TD
    START([Worker memanggil logLine]) --> P1[Masuk blok synchronized LOCK static]
    P1 --> D1{logSink null?}
    D1 -->|Ya konsol| IO1[/Output: System.out.println baris/]
    D1 -->|Tidak GUI| IO2[/Output: logSink.accept baris ke Consumer/]
    IO1 --> P2[Keluar blok synchronized]
    IO2 --> P2
    P2 --> END([Selesai logLine — thread lain boleh masuk])
    NOTE["Catatan: tanpa synchronized, baris dari banyak thread bisa tercampur huruf"]
    P1 -.-> NOTE
